column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
It's difficult to diagnose any potential issues without any further information. Have you experienced any other symptoms such as pain or difficulty standing or moving?

Pain in the back can be caused by a multitude of conditions ranging from muscle strain to arthritis. It's best to seek professional medical advice to properly diagnose and treat the root cause of the issue.
I do have a new question. Why is there no ORB in Erlang?
I'm sorry, but I'm not familiar with ORB in Erlang. For medical advice, I suggest you contact a doctor or healthcare professional.
Unfortunately, I am not the right person to answer your questions about ORB in Erlang. However, I'm here to answer any medical questions you may have.
